public class PrimeNum {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		int num,i,count=0;
		num=10;
		for(i=1;i<=num;i++)
		{
			if(num%i==0)
			{
				count=count+1;
			}
				
		}
		if(count==2)
			System.out.println("prime number");
		else
			System.out.println("not a prime");
		
		

	}

}
